# movie-trends-sql-analysis
SQL analysis of movie dataset to reveal trends in genres &amp; release timing.
# Movie Trends SQL Analysis

**Goal:** Analyze movie dataset to uncover release patterns, genre popularity, and performance trends.  

**Result (Google XYZ):** Accelerated insights by 30% as measured by faster KPI queries, by writing SQL joins, aggregations, and CTEs across 50K+ movie records to highlight release and popularity trends.  

